prompts.frontCover: Full body cartoon illustration of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, standing on a minimalist beach. They are illustrated in a simple, flat 2D style with clean lines and solid colors. Lao Lao (on the left) and Jordan (on the right) are in the same pose from the photo, smiling warmly. A tiny, very cute, brown and white Shiba Inu dog stands proudly between their feet, wearing a tiny birthday hat and holding a single red rose in its mouth, looking up at Lao Lao. The background is a simple, minimalist beach scene with a soft-colored sand stripe at the bottom and a gentle, light blue ocean stripe behind them under a clear sky. In the center of the card, in the sky area above the couple, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall composition is clean, centered, and charming.
